{"url": "https://www.dofus.com/en/mmorpg/encyclopedia/resources/11530-drilla-stone", "id": 11530, "name": "Drilla Stone", "img": "http://staticns.ankama.com/dofus/www/game/items/200/51466.png", "type": "Stone", "level": 187, "description": "It was inevitable that the Drilla would eventually find this stone as all he does is drill rock all day long. He is convinced that its odd appearance means it is worth more than a vulgar piece of coal, so he keeps it, and will almost certainly exchange it for a beer or perhaps a female goblin, although the beer would be a much better choice and far less hassle in the long term."}